snippet.title: Best VGM 1534 - Gunlord - Steel and Thunder (Holy Mountain I ~ Stage 1-1)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Neo Geo / Dreamcast / Wii U / 3DS
Gunlord (2012)
Steel and Thunder (Holy Mountain I ~ Stage 1-1)
Rafael Dyll
